Only 1 alarm per camera every 30 seconds is forwarded to the operator or ARC team.
🛠️ Can the timer be changed?
Yes. The redundancy timer is configurable per integration or device type. If you believe the default 30 seconds
is too long or too short, contact support to review your setup.
